{"article_id":"6IId9bTXzANcB8HF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"House Speaker Paul D. Ryan said Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that he will retire from the House at the end of this year ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"closing out a two-decade career in Congress","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and igniting soul-searching in a party","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"bracing for a rough election season .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Mr. Ryan rejected claims","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that he was fleeing a sinking ship .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"He predicted","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that Republicans will keep their House majority","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"despite headwinds in November ' s elections .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"He vowed to be an active lame-duck speaker","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"as he serves out his term ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"pushing for spending controls and the rest of the Republican agenda .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. Ryan said","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"his decision was about his family .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"He noted","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"that he came to Congress from Wisconsin","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"before his first child was born","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"and now all three children are teens .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"\" If I am here for one more term ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"my kids will only have ever known me as a weekend dad , \"","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"\" I just can ' t let that happen .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"So I will be setting new priorities in my life . \"","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"His announcement kicked off jockeying among Republicans","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"to fill his post .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"An informal push already had begun","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"as rumors of Mr. Ryan ' s retirement swirled .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"Top job in the House up for grabs","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"as Speaker Paul Ryan to retire","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy of California and Majority Whip Steve Scalise of Louisiana are seen as his most likely successors .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"Some lawmakers and conservative groups urged a go-slow approach","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"on choosing the next leader ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"particularly since Republicans ' position will not be clear until after November ' s elections .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"it ' s way too early for that , \"","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"said Rep. Scott Perry , Pennsylvania Republican .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"\" If Paul Ryan ' s not going to be here","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"and be the speaker ...","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"we ' re singularly focused on making sure","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Nancy Pelosi isn ' t the next speaker","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"- that ' s what we have to be . \"","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Ryan said","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Republican electoral prospects didn ' t enter his decision-making at all","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"and predicted","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that the party would retain its majority .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"he did consider proceeding with this election ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"so as not to feed stories of Republican despair ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"then resigning immediately afterward -","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"but he concluded","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"that would have been \" the normal politician thing . \"","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"\" In order to serve the people in my district honorably ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"I have to serve them honestly .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"And for me to ask them to vote","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"to re-elect me","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"knowing","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"that I wasn ' t going to stay","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"is not being honest , \"","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Mr. Ryan has been speaker for about 21⁄2 turbulent years .","depth":4},{"id":62,"text":"He faced down conservative rebellions","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"and secured a large tax cut ,","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"but he failed to repeal Obamacare or lock down a deal on immigration .","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"He said","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"he considered his biggest accomplishments to be tax cuts and last month ' s omnibus spending bill","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"that included a massive spike in Pentagon funding along with a big boost in domestic funding .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"His biggest regret ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"he said ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"was failing to win changes to big social spending programs","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"- though he said","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"the House , under his leadership as a committee chairman and then as speaker , had done its part","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"by passing \" the biggest entitlement reform bill","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"ever considered in the House of Representatives . \"","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Mr. Ryan , the Republican Party ' s 2012 vice presidential nominee , said","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"he thinks","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"he is finished with elected politics for the immediate future","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"- and potentially for good .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"\" Right now , the last thing","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"I ' m thinking about","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"is running for something , \"","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"he said on CNN .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"\" No plans","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"to run for anything ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"and I really don ' t think","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"I ' ll change my mind . \"","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"After serving as a prominent critic of Donald Trump at times during the 2016 campaign ,","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"he became the president ' s most effective ally on Capitol Hill","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"by helping push the White House agenda .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"\" Speaker Paul Ryan is a truly good man ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"while he will not be seeking re-election ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"he will leave a legacy of achievement","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"that nobody can question .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"We are with you Paul ! \"","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"Mr. Trump tweeted","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"after the news broke .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Democrats said","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"they hoped","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"that Mr. Ryan , free from having to face voters , will now turn against Mr. Trump","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"and sideline conservatives","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"who have resisted efforts","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"to strike more liberal-leaning deals .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"\" When you have so many intransigent people in your caucus","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"who say ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"' It ' s my way or no way , '","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"and your job ,","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"even though you have deep beliefs ,","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"is to get something done ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"it ' s hard .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"It ' s hard , \"","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"said Senate Minority Leader Charles E. Schumer , New York Democrat .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"Though Mr. Ryan soared to national prominence after 2010 with his budget blueprints","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that called for deep cuts to federal spending and major reforms to entitlement programs ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"his relationship with conservatives as speaker has been uneasy at times .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"In addition to spending concerns , some members of the House ' s right flank have said","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"Mr. Ryan hasn ' t lived up to pledges","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"to take a more bottom-up approach , with more input from the rank and file , than Speaker John A. Boehner ' s top-down approach .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"Adam Brandon , president of the conservative activist group FreedomWorks , praised Mr. Ryan ' s work","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"in securing the tax cut","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"but said","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"the next speaker \" must be willing to fight for real spending cuts and a return to regular order . \"","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"\" The status quo of the Republican Party is not sustainable , \"","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"said Mr. Brandon ,","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"adding","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"that the next speaker has to work with conservatives","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"\" to make the GOP the party of free markets and limited government again . \"","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"Rep. Mark Meadows , North Carolina Republican , said","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"he didn ' t necessarily see the next speaker coming from the House Freedom Caucus , a group of about three dozen hard-line conservatives","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"that has clashed with Mr. Ryan in recent years over issues such as immigration and federal spending .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"\" But certainly the Freedom Caucus having a voice in leadership decisions and the agenda is important , \"","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"said Mr. Meadows , the caucus chairman ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"while cautioning","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that a leadership position has never been on his own \" bucket list . \"","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Conservative members on Wednesday generally praised Mr. Ryan for his approach to the job and for helping win tax cuts last year .","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"They said","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"they would leave a more broad-based examination of his record for another time .","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"\" While there are occasions","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"where we have disagreements ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"obviously , he ' s still the leader of the House here","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"and he ' s open to conversation ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"and we appreciate that , \"","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"Mr. Perry said .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"\" I fully expect","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"for the duration of his term , he ' s going to be here","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"and lead","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"and we ' re going to obviously provide input ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"likely have some differences along the way [ until ] the end , \"","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"\" He ' s still here","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"leading . \"","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"Still , Rep. Walter B. Jones , North Carolina Republican , said","depth":6},{"id":153,"text":"part of Mr. Ryan ' s legacy will be the ballooning federal debt and deficits .","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"\" The tax bill ' s not paid for , \"","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"noting","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"that independent budget watchdogs have said","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"it could add as much as $ 2 trillion to the national debt over 10 years .","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"He also said","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"that either way , Congress wasn ' t shaping up","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"to do much for the rest of the year .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"\" I ' m not sure","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"we would have done much","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"if he didn ' t make the announcement today , \"","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"\" We haven ' t done much at all . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":333,"left":2